<function>

access:   public

name: anchorImage

param: Solar_Uri|string, $spec

param: string, $src

param: array, $attribs, array ()

return: string

</function>

Returns an image wrapped by an anchor href tag.

* Parameters:

 * Solar_Uri|string //$spec//: The anchor href specification.

 * string //$src//: The href to the image source.

 * array //$attribs//: Additional attributes for the image.

* Returns string: An <a href="..."><img ... /></a> tag set.